  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/28109b051a195684d98c38b876d3dfb9.avif?t=1738029562\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/4a68631b697108cedb89a127abdd37ad.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span> ： <br>This is a cute, casual, and fast-paced arcade pinball game .Cats love you more when you combo </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/4609ff064880150322c6f0b9761f8f1d.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span> ： <br>Many challenges await you to complete. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/dca79d1fc48c1b5df37b36e46eb369c3.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span>： <br>Let's play and be friends with cats. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/5b730439c667fad0f203aa6ea6487547.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span>： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge high scores. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/81bdeaa0f3061aac69c24a36b3df8e03.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span>： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently, there are 5 themes, and in the future, there will be free updates on gameplay and themes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Mode Gameplay Introduction:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/359526844e8f033a91028ed4538a2b2e.webp?t=1738029562\" width=246 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Continuously challenge to achieve the highest friendship level with the cat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/da03c208c90012ca8d8e93ae3229a83b.avif?t=1738029562\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras_big/da03c208c90012ca8d8e93ae3229a83b.avif?t=1738029562 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/f428441b5d63a98fe583d87c60bd5b74.webp?t=1738029562\" width=246 height=45 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the target friendship level within the given time and level up to 20 to win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/9c8ea16ea865bb61e60ed9b8e7537b3b.avif?t=1738029562\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras_big/9c8ea16ea865bb61e60ed9b8e7537b3b.avif?t=1738029562 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/76198c650188fa006d6810d367b0b11f.webp?t=1738029562\" width=246 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish with the cat and complete the fishing encyclopedia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.stea